headline: Leidos Welcomes Nearly 900 Summer Interns from 290 Colleges and Universities
summary: Every day, Leidos (NYSE: LDOS) employees tackle customers' most vexing challenges in defense, homeland security, information technology, intelligence, health, energy, and more. This summer in the U.S., nearly 900 summer interns from 290 colleges and universities are gaining valuable experience working across all aspects of the technology company's operations.
